name: Complex (Homebrew)
overview: You must try to get through all the caves and find the exit. To achieve this, you must search for and pick up a lot of things located in some of the caves. There are 25 different caves, and 5 ways to move, depending on which screen you are in. the name of the cave can be a great help in figuring things out! Good luck. Action game created by Terje Christiansen and released in 1987.
